Title: Custom Graphs timeseries transformation percentile
Level: 1
Component: metrics
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0b6
Date: 1565618826

Custom Graphs now support timeseries transformations. Now one can calculate
the percentile of a given timeseries. Just go to the custom graph designer
and pick a metric. The transformations field will activate imediately and
let you choose the option: Percentile within the timerange.

Configure which percentile you want. Integer from 0 to 100 and click the
button: Apply transform.
